A '''Crossbow stock''' is the wooden centre of a [[crossbow (weapon)|crossbow]]. It is required to make a crossbow. They can be [[Fletching|fletched]] by [[members]] who have the necessary Fletching level. They can also be purchased or stolen from the [[crossbow Shop (Keldagrim)|crossbow stall]] in [[Keldagrim]].

